{"tid":2509132,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"德將派軍艦赴亞洲   但避開台海　議員批對中跪低","createTime":"2021-04-29T08:27:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T08:54:38.000Z","uid":204533,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2386821ba99c62cb684f397f31204ad038fbb19d","tid":2509132,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T08:27:04.000Z","msg":"德國下半年將派軍艦到亞洲，回程時穿越南海，不過，為避免得罪北京，這艘軍艦將避開台灣海峽，引起國會友台議員不滿，直批這是向中國「磕頭」。<br />\n<br />\n25日出刊的德國《周日世界報》（Welt Am Sonntag）報導，德國政府認定台灣海峽是國際海域，不過<strong><span class=\"red\">根據國防部的規劃，即將啟程前往亞洲的巡防艦「巴伐利亞」（Bayern）號將不會通過台灣海峽。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n去年9月，德國首度針對印度太平洋地區擬定完整的外交方針，準備積極參與亞洲事務，並規劃今年8月派遣巡防艦到澳洲、朝鮮半島和南海，與澳洲、日本和美國等盟邦進行演習。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">國防部長康坎鮑爾（Annegret Kramp-Karrenbauer ）表示，派艦目的是確保航道自由和領土完整，並向美國釋出訊號。<br />\n<br />\n不過，報導指出，為了避免得罪北京，德國海軍這艘巡防艦將會避開台灣海峽。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n德艦刻意繞過台海，引起國會友台議員的不滿。自民黨（FDP）議員雷希特 （Ulrich Lechte）表示，通過台海象徵對台灣自由和民主的支持；反之，避開則是向中國「磕頭」，德國打算積極投入印太卻又磕頭，實在令人意外。（中央社）"},{"pid":"e1a3646f1f9d213d2be8605593120a906a08b862","tid":2509132,"uid":204533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T08:28:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210429/AEVB2JAXYNFQTB7CVMZSJIFQOY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210429%2FAEVB2JAXYNFQTB7CVMZSJIFQOY%2F&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwRphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=d40c8df6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210429%2FAEVB2JAXYNFQTB7CVMZSJIFQOY%2F&h=a70bd28c\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210429/AEVB2JAXYNFQTB7CVMZSJIFQOY/</a>"},{"pid":"470819dd50685fb8c9f3b0132075787c5b7a9963","tid":2509132,"uid":26834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T08:29:32.000Z","msg":"德國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf501817467fdde1971b387975089cb8d8f7dbfa","tid":2509132,"uid":329977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T08:30:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmetPyTdbD22AZDsf9hcRPyREfcunrhtZim5qozrzUfgZh?filename=mjfrzS8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmjfrzS8.gif&h=ae5a746a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4a514a4fec61553cf3ea3f982e3a67ab95d5ba0b","tid":2509132,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"470819dd50685fb8c9f3b0132075787c5b7a9963","tid":2509132,"uid":26834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T08:29:32.000Z","msg":"德國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T08:35:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0768ae013172a6a46ed7f61d243aec1012f3ab55","tid":2509132,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T08:49:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df88c4ab8bb0af77b5a69da70fb522b64cf77cdf","tid":2509132,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T08:50:10.000Z","msg":"二戰後德國廢足咁耐"},{"pid":"46025548783fefb15c9364de62f6a5a33265e77f","tid":2509132,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T08:51:47.000Z","msg":"算把啦，德軍垃圾嚟"},{"pid":"e926d0e04ec931997aa7b78209ba0b3b652c9abd","tid":2509132,"uid":83609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T08:52:57.000Z","msg":"又跪<br />\n咁仲派咩艦隊遊船河呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" clas